@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pdthzf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.97) - v1) + wp.exp(0.29))
    tmp = v2
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.08)) * 0.53)
    v1 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.94 * v1 + 0.77)) - (wp.exp(v2 + 0.65) * (v0 + 0.20 * v1 + 0.35)))
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.exp(v1 + 0.20) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.41)))
    data[tid] = v0
